<plot>The metaphor of blacksmithing parallels the hardship and isolation Yelena feels in her marriage. Keeping her true feelings hidden, she holds on to one dream. Director Svetlana Cvetko brings this expressive story to a circular ending that leaves the audience feeling that what they have seen is just another day in Yelena's hard life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?491404</url></doc>
